      "span_id": "p031_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0002",
      "text": " 12",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0003",
      "text": "b) State transitions are logically instantaneous, so the only actions taken during a transition are",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        321.65,
        539.92,
        332.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0004",
      "text": "setting flags and variables and sending signals. These actions complete before the next state",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        333.65,
        539.96,
        344.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0005",
      "text": "is entered.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        345.65,
        169.03,
        356.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0006",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        370.97,
        114.35,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0007",
      "text": "Every time a state is entered, the actions of that state are started. Note that this means that a",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        370.97,
        539.98,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0008",
      "text": "transition that points back to the same state repeats the actions from the beginning. All the ac-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        382.97,
        540.01,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0009",
      "text": "tions started upon entry complete before any tests are made to exit the state.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        394.97,
        462.36,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0010",
      "text": "d) When Virtual Fabrics are used there is a different state for each Virtual Fabric negotiated to be",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        418.97,
        540.05,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p031_s0011",
      "text": "used on a link. The state Px for Virtual Fabric K is denoted Px(k).",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.97,
        408.99,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
